Personal Instance Rules:
1. In Personal Instances, you'll get most of the Evolution Equipment and corresponding fragments;
2. Chances for Personal Instances are limited, you can buy extra chances and the price will be gradually increased;
3. Personal Instance will consume Vitality and according to Instance level, Vitality consumption will gradually increase;
4. In Personal Instance, the challenge chances for each stage will be calculated respectively.

Instance rules:
1. You can get part of Evolution Equipment Fragments in Instances;
2. Daily Instance chances are limited and you're not allowed to buy extra chances;
3. Instance challenge chances are respectively calculated for each stage, you can enter multiple stages simultaneously;
4. Instance won't consume Vitality while stages will consume Activity to open and reset;
5. After Instances are opened, guild member with last hit will receive extra rewards;
6. All attending guild members will receive extra rewards if they have cleared an Instance within time limit;
7. Guild members shall queue for Guild Instance Loots, and the loots will be sent via in-game mail;
8. There'll be damage stats for each stage, the last stage of an Instance will calculate double stats and, according to damage rankings, all attending guild members will receive extra rewards.

1. Defeat the monsters in Zanpakuto according to the storyline;
2. There are 4 difficulty levels in this campaign: Normal ,Hard ,Nightmare ,Inferno ;
3. You can select 1 difficulty to conduct your challenge each time;
4. There're 15 stages for each difficulty and the rewards are based on the difficulty you selected;
5. There'll be finishing rewards and they'll be sent via in-game mail.

